  <thing id="mS2Leafwea" name="Leafweave" description="The artisans of Aerenal weave suits of armor from bronzewood leaves, which are then treated by a special alchemical process that makes them as tough and fl exible as leather, with considerably less weight and encumbrance.{br}{br}Creating leafweave armor requires a DC 25 Craft (alchemy) check in addition to the normal Craft (armorsmithing) checks required to make armor." compset="Armor">
