  <thing id="gS2AlchSpa" name="Alchemist&apos;s Spark" description="Alchemist&apos;s spark combines two substances that react violently when mixed. A fl ask of alchemist&apos;s spark has two compartments that keep the two substances separate; throwing the fl ask shatters it and allows the substances to mix, releasing a powerful electrical discharge. Otherwise, alchemist&apos;s spark functions like alchemist&apos;s fi re except that it deals 1d8 points of electricity damage on a direct hit (and 1 point of electricity damage to those it splashes), rather than fi re damage. It deals no additional damage after the initial damage." compset="Gear">
