  <thing id="gS2NoxSmok" name="Noxious Smokestick" description="A variation on the common smokestick, this object pours forth extremely foul-smelling smoke when it is ignited. In addition to the obscuring effects of a smokestick, a creature within the smoke of a noxious smokestick must make a DC 15 Fortitude saving throw or be nauseated for 1 round." compset="Gear" stacking="merge">
