  <thing id="gS2Glyphbo" name="Glyphbook" description="Despite its name, this book offers no help in dealing with magical {i}glyphs of warding.{/i} Rather, it is a guide to the ancient scripts of Xen&apos;drik, useful in deciphering inscriptions found within the cyclopean ruins that litter that continent. Far from complete or comprehensive, a glyph book presumes a certain familiarity with ancient scripts to begin with (at least 1 rank in Linguistics). It grants a +4 circumstance bonus on Linguistics checks made to read inscriptions in Xen&apos;drik ruins." compset="Gear">
