  <thing id="ipS2wEarth" name="Earthbound" description="An earthbound weapon has a Small earth elemental bound to it, and has a heavy, crystalline appearance. As long as the wielder and his opponent are both touching the ground, the weapon grants its wielder an additional +2 bonus on attack and damage rolls. If the wielder is flying, the weapon&apos;s enhancement bonus from this property does not apply to his attacks (though the +1 enhancement bonus on his attack and damage rolls for using a magical weapon still applies)." compset="ItemPower" summary="Weapon deals +2H/D if both you and your opponent are touching the ground." uniqueness="useronce">
