  <thing id="ipS2wFines" name="Finesse" description="A finesse weapon has a Small air elemental bound to it, and has a slightly translucent appearance. This property can be applied only to a light weapon, a rapier, a whip, or a spiked chain, and its benefits apply only if the wielder is the size of creature that the weapon was made for. The wielder can use a finesse weapon as if he had the Weapon Finesse feat. In addition, the weapon grants a +2 enhancement bonus to the wielder&apos;s Dexterity score." compset="ItemPower" summary="You weield this weapon as if you had the Weapon Finesse feat." uniqueness="useronce">
