  <thing id="ioS2Armbla" name="Armblade" description="{B}Component Type:{/b}  Attached component\n\nThis large metal cylinder with a heavy, serrated sword blade at one end attaches to a warforged. It fits over the hand and forearm. An {i}armblade{/i} is a {i}+1 bastard sword{/i}, and requires the Exotic Weapon Proficiency (bastard sword) feat to use it properly. While the weapon is attached, the warforged cannot be disarmed, but the warforged also cannot use that hand for other tasks without removing the {i}armblade{/i}. In addition, the wielder gains a +2 bonus on CMB vs disarm. If the wielder uses a ready action to set an {i}armblade{/i} against a charge, he deals double damage on a successful hit against a charging character." compset="Wondrous">
