  <thing id="ipS2OilRLD" name="Oil of Repair Light Damage" description="During the Last War, the defenders of Cyre relied heavily on the use of warforged and other constructs, but it was impossible to have an artificer in every unit. {i}Oil of repair{/i} was developed to provide emergency assistance to units protecting critical regions. This oil acts just like the relevant {i}repair damage{/i} spell." compset="OilPotion" stacking="merge">
