  <thing id="irS2CirSou" name="Circle of Sound" description="These magical rings are made in sets of two to six. By whispering into one of these rings, the wearer can send a message to everyone wearing a ring from the same set. The range of this effect is 220 feet, and it has all the restrictions and advantages of the {i}message{/i} spell. While the cost of these rings is prohibitively expensive for most people, Aurum mercenaries and similarly wealthy soldiers often make use of them.\n\nOnce a set of {i}circles of sound{/i} has been forged, there is no way to add additional rings to the circuit." compset="Ring">
