  <thing id="minS2Clfoo" name="Clawfoot" description="A human-sized predator of the Talenta Plains, this dinosaur is the halfl ing equivalent of a warhorse. Well trained and loyal, a clawfoot often continues fighting even after its rider&apos;s death. While a clawfoot would be considered exotic on many worlds, an exotic saddle is not required for riding one." compset="Minion">
